TCPSER license notice
=====================

Source: https://github.com/go4retro/tcpser

The upstream README states:

  TCPSER is distributed under the GPL 2.0 or later

The BMX tree imports a small TCPSER modem-core subset and replaces the original
POSIX serial/TCP I/O layer with the BMX bare-metal adapter. The imported subset
is therefore used under GPL-2.0-or-later.

The full GNU General Public License version 2 text is available in the BMX
source tree at:

  third_party/vice-3.10/COPYING
